'''阿尔忒弥斯1號'''（{{lang-en|Artemis I}}）<ref>{{cite report |title=Artemis : brand book |location=Washington, D.C. |publisher=National Aeronautics and Space Administration |date=2019 |id=NP-2019-07-2735-HQ |quote=MISSION NAMING CONVENTION. While Apollo mission patches used numbers and roman numerals throughout the program, Artemis mission names will use a roman numeral convention. }}</ref>是[[NASA|NASA]]的[[阿提米絲計畫|阿提米絲計畫]]的無載人試驗飛行，這是該機構的[[獵戶座太空船|獵戶座MPCV]]和[[太空發射系統|太空發射系統]]重型火箭的首次綜合飛行。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/17/18627839/nasa-administrator-jim-bridenstine-artemis-moon-program-budget-amendment|title=NASA administrator on new Moon plan: 'We're doing this in a way that's never been done before'|last=Grush|first=Loren|date=2019-05-17|work=The Verge|access-date=2019-05-17|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704091616/https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/17/18627839/nasa-administrator-jim-bridenstine-artemis-moon-program-budget-amendment|dead-url=no}}</ref>
截至2022年5月，阿尔忒弥斯1号预计将不早于2022年8月发射。<ref name="sfn-20220426">{{cite web |last=Clark |first=Stephen |url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2022/04/26/nasas-moon-rocket-rolls-back-to-vehicle-assembly-building-for-repairs/ |title=NASA's moon rocket rolls back to Vehicle Assembly Building for repairs |work=Spaceflight Now |date=2022-04-26 |access-date=2022-04-26}}</ref>

以前稱為'''探索任務1號'''（{{lang-en|Exploration Mission-1, EM-1}}），在[[阿提米絲計畫|阿提米絲計畫]]成形後重新命名。发射将在[[肯尼迪航天中心|肯尼迪航天中心]]{{le|肯尼迪航天中心39B号发射台|Kennedy Space Center Launch Complex 39B|39B号发射台}}进行，在猎户座飞船执行的26-42天任务中，6天对[[月球|月球]]轨道进行逆向环绕<ref>{{Cite web|title=NASA's Space Launch System Begins Integration in Preparation for Launch|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.2514/6.2021-4226.vid|access-date=2022-03-23|date=2021-11-08|work=dx.doi.org}}</ref>。该任务将为接下来[[阿尔忒弥斯2号|阿尔忒弥斯2号]]的猎户座及太空发射系统的第二次载人飞行进行测试<ref>{{Cite web|title=NASA will likely add a rendezvous test to the first piloted Orion space mission|url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2020/05/18/nasa-will-likely-add-a-rendezvous-test-to-the-first-piloted-orion-space-mission/|access-date=2022-03-23|author=Stephen Clark|date=2020-05-18|language=English}}</ref>。

阿尔忒弥斯1号的猎户座飞船与2021年10月20日移至[[航天器裝配大樓|航天器装配大楼]]（VAB），开始自[[天空实验室|天空实验室]]的[[土星5号运载火箭|土星5号]]后总装大楼内的首次超重型运载火箭安装<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stacking of Orion spacecraft caps assembly of first Artemis moon rocket|url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2021/10/21/stacking-of-orion-spacecraft-caps-assembly-of-first-artemis-moon-rocket/|access-date=2022-03-22|author=Stephen Clark|date=2021-10-21}}</ref>。

